Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.49,0:22:45.04,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}溢れてく　See, I don't want to lose to my self
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:53.31,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}止めないで　Now I wanna know. Set me free
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:23:00.22,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Tell me Tell me Tell me　繰り返した
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.23,0:23:04.42,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What's happening here?　鏡の中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:12.83,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}心を凍らせた知らない自分が微笑む
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.86,0:23:17.12,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}鏡　鏡　鏡　引き返せない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.13,0:23:21.48,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}What's calling out here?　影に揺れる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:29.64,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}不実に絡まった　鎖をどうか外して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:34.65,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I find my way out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:38.65,BG-edj,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}'Cause your way will stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:23.45,BG-edc,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}辨别中的Whiteout  渐渐扭曲成幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.98,0:22:28.35,BG-edc,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}对发出询问的气息  产生了共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.48,0:22:31.79,BG-edc,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}逐渐加速的Flashback  在探寻着这份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:36.04,BG-edc,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I just live by my raison d'être
